				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Scarlet Envelope: Wild Mansion of Mr.Ferri" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>This is the fifth game in the series of &amp;quot;Scarlet Envelope&amp;quot; games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This tabletop escape room game tells a mysterious story of Mr.Ferri, the extravagant animal lover and the owner of the creepiest mansion in town, who has suddenly passed away. The word on the street is that he was killed&amp;hellip;by his own lion! But&amp;hellip;was he really? And why is his wife hiring you to get him back home, while his son is talking to Ferri&amp;rsquo;s spirit through the ouija board? Looks like we've got another mystery on our hands!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAME CONTENTS:&amp;#10;- Mysterious paper-based Ouija spirit board&amp;#10;- Photo from the Ferri mansion dining room&amp;#10;- Three cryptic polaroid photos&amp;#10;- Letter from Mr.Ferri's wife&amp;#10;- Greeting card with a condolence message&amp;#10;- Private investigator's report&amp;#10;- Voicemail message, audio files&amp;#10;- Emailing the character to get extra digital files&amp;#10;- Web safe box to unlock online&amp;#10;- Instructions and Online Hints in case you're stuck&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game features some very unusual special effects! The story is packed with puzzles. You need a device with an Internet connection + we recommend playing at home (you'll understand why). Roughly 2 hours of gameplay. Two levels of difficulty available.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
